<section class="blog-post why-choose">
    <div class="row fadeLeftRight">
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-8 fadeLeftEffect">
            <img src="../Content/Images/Earth.jpg">
            <a href="#">
                <img src="../Content/Images/link.png">
                Bringing New Technology
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 fadeRightEffect">
            <div class="post">
                <h3>WHY CHOOSE</h3>
                <h2>OHNI</h2>
                <p>
                    Our project will deliver data through localized blockchains
                    with IOT system through mobile phones, harnessing billions of
                    devices for fluent processing. Our project is entirely anonymous 
                    and open source and we plan on rewarding people for working on our 
                    project and learning to code because we believe in building it 
                    right the first time, from the ground up. Implementing a new peer-to-peer 
                    banking system, individuals and communities make their priorities visible
                    to the business community. Instead of a debt-based system, the Ohni ecosystem
                    allows individual and community-organized lending to generate assets for
                    consumer consumption and community projects. These are documented through the OBT.
                </p>
                <a href="#" class="default"><i class="fa fa-long-arrow-right"></i> ABOUT OHNI</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="benefits">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4 fadeUpEffect wait05">
