                    <h4>INTEREST FREE</h4>
                    <p>
                        People with the Ohni Bank Token (OBT) will not generate money
                        with interest but rather fractional reserve banking. With Ohni
                        Consumer Coin (OCC) balances being kept on the OBT, a OBT user
                        can ask a fraction of their users for their balances, multiply them
                        and lend them out to projects for new technology, alternative energy,
                        robotics and charitable causes. Since loans are interest free, they will
                        be paid back over time.
                    </p>
                    <a href="#" class="default"><i class="fa fa-long-arrow-right"></i> SEE MORE</a>
