                    <p>
                        Since there will be a global blockchain of demand
                        on Ohni Corporate Servers (entirely anonymous),
                        in a series of images, machine learning can process
                        where demand should go. This would make Ohni the world's
                        first giant AI for humanity to decide how to save, conserve
                        and tap resources for a prosperous future. This AI will
                        be controlled and only decide on what to do with demand
